{"tid":1147710,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"批歐盟2018年香港報告不實　中國外交部：港人享有前所未有的權利和自由","createTime":"2019-05-10T04:11:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-10T04:23:15.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"17c7007d9dc7c015079b2aeea61768dd233992a8","tid":1147710,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T04:11:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190509/s00001/15b01dbcc644cef03a0eb5f2570fe4a9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190509%2Fs00001%2F15b01dbcc644cef03a0eb5f2570fe4a9.jpg&h=043bfa51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n歐盟外交和安全政策高級代表昨日（8日）就香港事務發表報告，提到「一國兩制」和港人的公民政治權利正被蠶食，令人憂慮香港作為國際金融中心的吸引力。外交部發言人耿爽今日（9日）回應，批評歐盟罔顧事實，對香港事務指手劃腳。<br />\n<br />\n耿爽在記者會中回應歐盟2018香港報告，表示香港居民「依法享有前所未有的民主權利和言論、新聞、結社等自由」，而報告對香港事務「妄加評論、指手劃腳」，是在粗暴干涉中國內政。耿爽強調，中方對此感到強烈不滿，並要求歐盟停止發表有關報告。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190509/s00001/1557391675208/批歐盟2018年香港報告不實-外交部-港人享有前所未有的權利和自由\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190509%2Fs00001%2F1557391675208%2F%E6%89%B9%E6%AD%90%E7%9B%9F2018%E5%B9%B4%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%A0%B1%E5%91%8A%E4%B8%8D%E5%AF%A6-%E5%A4%96%E4%BA%A4%E9%83%A8-%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E4%BA%AB%E6%9C%89%E5%89%8D%E6%89%80%E6%9C%AA%E6%9C%89%E7%9A%84%E6%AC%8A%E5%88%A9%E5%92%8C%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1&d=7bK604G145JEtCxDEZ4NGpgFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=3732ab04\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190509%2Fs00001%2F1557391675208%2F%E6%89%B9%E6%AD%90%E7%9B%9F2018%E5%B9%B4%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%A0%B1%E5%91%8A%E4%B8%8D%E5%AF%A6-%E5%A4%96%E4%BA%A4%E9%83%A8-%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E4%BA%AB%E6%9C%89%E5%89%8D%E6%89%80%E6%9C%AA%E6%9C%89%E7%9A%84%E6%AC%8A%E5%88%A9%E5%92%8C%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1&h=23e56b79\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190509/s00001/1557391675208/批歐盟2018年香港報告不實-外交部-港人享有前所未有的權利和自由</a>"},{"pid":"87ebb16aa464794abbded7b4ac1700996f3e77ae","tid":1147710,"uid":626,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T04:13:16.000Z","msg":"有時諗下, 佢份工都幾好做"},{"pid":"3b064972309cc20edcbb6d220cd5ee13661cd7b4","tid":1147710,"uid":58335,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T04:13:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcQ1K1FHR-BZ7wElGRwPulALG880dZ9bnYNbMTIWGmU1XQKIKpwZvw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%3AANd9GcQ1K1FHR-BZ7wElGRwPulALG880dZ9bnYNbMTIWGmU1XQKIKpwZvw&h=998a3caf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"430faafa4ed55d16e5db8521be966c5393757e3e","tid":1147710,"uid":11169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T04:23:15.000Z","msg":"唔識人權學人講人權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}